column5: Heard a rumour that there are huts on Gull Lake south of Minden....could anyone confirm this ???  THANKS in advance, Rook
Call a local Northern Rock Bait and tackle 5.0 (3) · Fishing camp 12818 ON-35 Unit 3 (705) 286-3242
You can call on your dime, https://www.gulllakehutrentals.ca/contact/
Thanks for the very quick responses !!! Much appreciated !!
I would be surprised if the guys were out. Also without checking I believe lakers are usually Jan 1 for opener.
